筛选开场白通常是发无意义的表情或者对话，来看待对方会不会回复你。
如果你没有提供任何话题，女孩还愿意和你聊天，那么说明对你有点兴趣。
如果你直接和女孩聊暧昧的话题，比如“爱妃，朕终于找到你了。”，女孩还愿意回复你，那么就代表女孩对你的兴趣是非常大的。
所以筛选开场白通常只是一个测试，属于简单粗暴的方式，但通常成功换来的回报会最大。
记住，它只是为了测试女孩对你的态度，而不能保证女孩会不会回复你。

通常情况下，女孩都会问你“什么事”。 
 
那这个时候就可以说想帮朋友买礼物，但我对这些化妆品不太懂，怕买的贵又不好，你知道那些品牌比较价格合理，而质量又不错的吗?
通常女孩一般没什么急事的话都会和你简单的介绍一下的，那就可以和她攀谈起来了。这个搭讪开场白适合在一些购物场所和百货商店。
适合新手使用，能有效的搭讪到对方，并且接下来，你们可以就化妆品的问题聊很久，还不会显得你很想搭讪对方。
最后以谢谢她的口吻，表达喜欢她的友善，收她的联系方式。
间接开场白最为灵活，根据当时的场景，用不同的方法和女孩女孩搭讪。
缺点：对于擦肩而过女孩，不容易迅速想到最自然的开场。碰到不友善的女孩，可能不会想回答你的问题。
优点：灵活自然，不会暴露自己太多的目的，还可以留下一个可以聊很久的话题。

对竞争对手调查的内容 ，可以包括A、竞争对手的数量与经营实力包括各个对手的产能、产量、性质、背景、销售量、销售额、经济实力、企业形象、经营历史、团队组成等。B、竞争对手的市场占有率
因竞争对手在不同的行政区域和行业领域的市场份额不尽相同，因此对其进行市场占有率计算时也要根据不同的区域和领域数据统计裁定。
C、竞争对手的竞争策略与手段
包括其销售渠道、物流、公关、服务、动态、回款周期与收款方式、营销人员的素质与职能、销售人员的工作模式等。
D、竞争对手的产品包括其产品价格、性能、质量、附加值、稳定性、产品组合等。
E、竞争对手的技术
包括各竞争对手原材料的采购、技术人员素质、研发实力与动向、生产设备、生产管理、生产人员素质等。
F、竞争对手的客户分布
包括对手的客户分布区域、行业侧重面、各区域市场的经营状态等。
调查渠道，可以包括：
1、行业报刊杂志与网络2、竞争对手的客户
3、竞争对手
4、下游产品销售市场或档口
5、本企业内部
6、各类展会
7、政府相关部门与行业机构

        <view wx:if="{{inputValue!=''}}">
          <icon type="clear" size="20" @tap="delText"></icon>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{showRecommend==0}}">
        <tab class="tab" @currentTab.user="getCurrentTab" :currentTab.sync="currentTab" :tabList.sync="tabList" ></tab>
      </view>
    </view>
    <swiper class="showdata" current="{{currentTab}}" bindchange="changeTab" wx:if="{{showRecommend==0}}" style="height: {{clientHeight+'rpx'}}">
      <swiper-item wx:for="{{[0,1,2]}}">
        <scroll-view scroll-y="true" style="height: {{clientHeight+'rpx'}}">
          <view class="view" wx:if="{{currentTab==0}}">
            <placeholder wx:if="{{huashuList.length==0}}" message="暂无数据"></placeholder>
            <huashu :huashuList.sync="huashuList"></huashu>
          </view>
          <view class="view" wx:if="{{currentTab==1}}">
            <placeholder wx:if="{{guanliList.length==0}}" message="暂无数据"></placeholder>
            <guanli :guanliList.sync="guanliList"></guanli>
          </view>
          <view class="view" wx:if="{{currentTab==2}}">
            <placeholder wx:if="{{biaoqingList.length==0}}" message="暂无数据"></placeholder>
            <biaoqing :biaoqingList.sync="biaoqingList"></biaoqing>
          </view>
        </scroll-view>
      </swiper-item>
    </swiper>
    <!--暂无数据显示-->
    <view wx:if="{{showRecommend}}">
      <view class="recommend">
        <view class="bigkuai">
          <view class="kuai">
            <view class="biaoti">热门推荐</view>
            <button class="weui-btn" type="default" size="mini" wx:for="{{hotWordsList}}" wx:key="item" @tap="searchKeyword0({{item}})">{{item}}</button>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="bigkuai">
          <view class="kuai">
            <view class="biaoti">方法搜索</view>
            <button class="weui-btn" type="default" size="mini" wx:for="{{hotMethodsList}}" wx:key="item" @tap="searchKeyword1({{item}})">{{item}}</button>
          </view>

          </view>
          <view class="if_his" wx:if="{{hisWordsList.length==0}}">暂无搜索记录</view>

<script>
  import wepy from 'wepy';
  import api from '@/api/api';
  import tip from '@/utils/tip'
  import tab from '@/components/tab'
  import {
    SYSTEM_INFO,
    USER_SPECICAL_INFO
  } from '@/utils/constant';
  import search from '@/components/search'
  import huashu from '@/components/huashu'
  import guanli from '@/components/guanli'
  import biaoqing from '@/components/biaoqing'
  import placeholder from "../components/placeholder"
  export default class searchPage extends wepy.page {
    config = {
      navigationBarTitleText: '搜索',
      enablePullDownRefresh:true,
      enableReachBottom:true,
    }
    components = {
      tab: tab,
      huashu : huashu,
      guanli : guanli,
      biaoqing : biaoqing,
      search: search,
      placeholder: placeholder
    }
    data = {
      clientHeight:0,
      focus:false,
      firstShow:true,
      inputValue:"",
      currentTab:0,
      huashuList:[],
      guanliList:[],
      biaoqingList:[],
      tabList:['话术','惯例','表情'],
      hisWordsList: [],
      hotWordsList:[],
      hotMethodsList:[],
      showRecommend: false,
    }
    async getRecommend() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getRecommend({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hotWordsList = json.data.data.hotWordsList;
      this.hotMethodsList = json.data.data.hotMethodsList;
      this.$apply();
    }
    async getHiswordList() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getHiswordList({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hisWordsList = json.data.data;
      this.$apply();
    }
    computed = {}
    async getSearch() {
      let that = this;
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getSearch({
        query: {
          query: that.inputValue,
          openid:openid,
        }
      });
      if(json.data.MSG=='OK'){
        that.huashuList = json.data.data.huashuList;
        that.guanliList = json.data.data.guanliList;
        that.biaoqingList = json.data.data.biaoqingList;
      }
      else{
        tip.confirm('您今天的搜索次数达到上限，请明天再来~');
      }
      that.showRecommend = false;
      that.getHiswordList();
      that.$apply();
    }
    async clearHiswords() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.clearHiswords({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hisWordsList = [];
      this.$apply();
    }
    doSearch(val) {
      val=val.replace(/^\s\s*/, '').replace(/\s\s*$/, '');
      if(val.length){
        this.inputValue = val;
        this.getSearch();
        this.$apply();
      }
    }
    onPullDownRefresh() {
      let that=this;
      if(that.showRecommend)
        that.showRecommend=false;
      else{
        that.focus=true;
        that.showRecommend=true;
      }
      wx.stopPullDownRefresh();
      that.$apply();
    }
    onShareAppMessage() {
      return {
        title: '恋爱助理',
        path: '/pages/home',
      };
    }
    onLoad() {
      let that = this;
      wx.getSystemInfo({
        success: function (res) {
          that.clientHeight=res.windowHeight*750/res.windowWidth-142;
        }
      });
      wx.getClipboardData({
        success: function(res){
          that.doSearch(res.data);
        }
      })
      that.getRecommend();
      that.getHiswordList();
      that.$apply();
    }
    setfirstShow(){
      this.firstShow=false;
      this.$apply();
    }
    onShow() {
      let that=this;
      if(that.firstShow){
        that.setfirstShow();
      }
      else{
        wx.getClipboardData({
          success: function(res){
            that.doSearch(res.data);
          }
        })
      }
      that.$apply();
    }
    changeTab(e) {
      if(e.detail.source.length)
        this.currentTab=e.detail.current;
      this.$apply();
    }
    methods = {
      bindinput(obj){
        this.inputValue = obj.detail.value;
      },
      bindconfirm(){
        this.showRecommend = false;
        this.doSearch(this.inputValue);
      },
      bindfocus(){
        this.showRecommend=true;
      },
      delText() {
        this.inputValue = "";
      },
      getCurrentTab(cur, evt){
        this.currentTab=cur;
      },
      searchKeyword0(val){
        this.currentTab=0;
        this.doSearch(val);
      },
      searchKeyword1(val){
        this.currentTab=1;
        this.doSearch(val);
      },
      clearHis() {
        this.clearHiswords();
      },
    }
  }
</script>

      tabList:['话术','惯例','表情'],
      hisWordsList: [],
      hotWordsList:[],
      hotMethodsList:[],
      showRecommend: false,
    }
    async getRecommend() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getRecommend({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hotWordsList = json.data.data.hotWordsList;
      this.hotMethodsList = json.data.data.hotMethodsList;

    async getHiswordList() {

        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hisWordsList = json.data.data;
      this.$apply();
    }
    computed = {}
    async getSearch() {
      let that = this;
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getSearch({
        query: {
          query: that.inputValue,
          openid:openid,
        }
      });
      if(json.data.MSG=='OK'){
        that.huashuList = json.data.data.huashuList;
        that.guanliList = json.data.data.guanliList;

  export default class searchPage extends wepy.page {
    config = {
      navigationBarTitleText: '搜索',
      enablePullDownRefresh:true,
      enableReachBottom:true,
    }
    components = {
      tab: tab,
      huashu : huashu,
      guanli : guanli,
      biaoqing : biaoqing,
      search: search,
    }
    data = {
      clientHeight:0,
      focus:false,
      firstShow:true,
      inputValue:"",
      currentTab:0,
      huashuList:[],
      guanliList:[],
      biaoqingList:[],
      tabList:['话术','惯例','表情'],
      hisWordsList: [],
      hotWordsList:[],
      hotMethodsList:[],
      showRecommend: false,
    }
    async getRecommend() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getRecommend({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hotWordsList = json.data.data.hotWordsList;
      this.hotMethodsList = json.data.data.hotMethodsList;
      this.$apply();
    }
    async getHiswordList() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getHiswordList({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hisWordsList = json.data.data;
      this.$apply();
    }
    computed = {}
    async getSearch() {
      let that = this;
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.getSearch({
        query: {
          query: that.inputValue,
          openid:openid,
        }
      });
      if(json.data.MSG=='OK'){
        that.huashuList = json.data.data.huashuList;
        that.guanliList = json.data.data.guanliList;
        that.biaoqingList = json.data.data.biaoqingList;
      }
      else{
        tip.confirm('您今天的搜索次数达到上限，请明天再来~');
      }
      that.showRecommend = false;
      that.getHiswordList();
      that.$apply();
    }
    async clearHiswords() {
      let userSpecialInfo = wepy.getStorageSync(USER_SPECICAL_INFO) || {};
      let openid = userSpecialInfo.openid;
      const json = await api.clearHiswords({
        query: {
          openid: openid
        }
      });
      this.hisWordsList = [];
      this.$apply();
    }
    doSearch(val) {
      val=val.replace(/^\s\s*/, '').replace(/\s\s*$/, '');
      if(val.length){
        this.inputValue = val;
        this.getSearch();
        this.$apply();
      }
    }
    onPullDownRefresh() {
      let that=this;
      if(that.showRecommend)
        that.showRecommend=false;
      else{
        that.focus=true;
        that.showRecommend=true;
      }
      wx.stopPullDownRefresh();
      that.$apply();
    }
    onShareAppMessage() {
      return {
        title: '恋爱助理',
        path: '/pages/home',
      };
    }
    onLoad() {
      let that = this;
      wx.getSystemInfo({
        success: function (res) {
          that.clientHeight=res.windowHeight*750/res.windowWidth-142;
        }
      });
      wx.getClipboardData({
        success: function(res){
          that.doSearch(res.data);
        }
      })
      that.getRecommend();
      that.getHiswordList();
      that.$apply();
    }
    setfirstShow(){
      this.firstShow=false;
      this.$apply();
    }
    onShow() {
      let that=this;
      if(that.firstShow){
        that.setfirstShow();
      }
      else{
        wx.getClipboardData({
          success: function(res){
            that.doSearch(res.data);
          }
        })
      }
      that.$apply();
    }
    changeTab(e) {
      if(e.detail.source.length)
        this.currentTab=e.detail.current;
      this.$apply();
    }
    methods = {
      bindinput(obj){
        this.inputValue = obj.detail.value;
      },
      bindconfirm(){
        this.showRecommend = false;
        this.doSearch(this.inputValue);
      },
      bindfocus(){
        this.showRecommend=true;
      },
      delText() {
        this.inputValue = "";
      },
      getCurrentTab(cur, evt){
        this.currentTab=cur;
      },
      searchKeyword0(val){
        this.currentTab=0;
        this.doSearch(val);
      },
      searchKeyword1(val){
        this.currentTab=1;
        this.doSearch(val);
      },
      clearHis() {
        this.clearHiswords();
      },
    }
  }
</script>
